data.title: A+ (atheism plus), For A Third Glorious Age of Total Agreement
data.meta_description: "New Atheism" was built on the backs of heavyweights who had all written hard hitting best sellers. The social fabric was shaken by the approach of Harris, Hitchens, Dawkins and Dennet, appropriately dubbed no less than 'the four horsemen'.
